<TEXT>
   A 3-year-old child has died of injuries he
suffered when he was mauled by a pit bull terrier owned by his
grandparents, authorities said.
   Dustin Webb, son of Steve and Debbie Webb, died Thursday at John
Sealy Hospital in nearby Galveston, a day after he was attacked by
